Title: Jose Chung's 'From Outer Space'
Plot: A alien abduction of two teenagers with endless versions of the same story prompts a science-fiction novelist to to write a book about the incident; however, nobody involved with the investigation can tell him the full story with any accuracy.
GuestStars: Charles Nelson Reilly, William Lucking, Larry Musser, Daniel Quinn, Jesse Ventura, Jason Gaffney, Sarah Sawatsky, Allan Zinyk, Alex Diakun, Andrew Turner, Michael Dobson, Japp Broeker, Alex Trebek
